  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Dialog: Pulley</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;">Pulley</para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso" style="margin-left:0px;">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddPulley">Add Pulley</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">A <text styleclass="Element-Header">Pulley</text> is a wheel with teeth that engage with a toothed-belt. The belt wraps around the <text styleclass="Element-Header">pulley</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You control the path of the belt with a <text styleclass="VariableName">sketch-loop</text><text styleclass="Body Text">. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You control the motion of the Pulley or Belt. </para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">The motion of the Belt controls the motion of the Pulley - a <text styleclass="VariableName">Driven-Pulley</text>.</li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">The motion of the Pulley controls the motion of the Belt - a Driving-Pulley. Maximum of one <text styleclass="VariableName">Driving-Pulley</text> per Belt.</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You control the motion of the belt with motion-values at the input-connector to a <text styleclass="Element">Motion-Path FB</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use the <text styleclass="Element-Header">Pulley</text><text styleclass="Element"> dialog</text> to edit the <text styleclass="ParameterHeader">number-of-teeth</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> on a </text><text styleclass="Element">Pulley</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">How to open the Pulley dialog</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:240px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-GA-DoubleClick-Pulley.png" scale="-99.90%" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Double-Click a Pulley]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">To edit the<text styleclass="Element"> Pulley</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Double-click a </text><text styleclass="Element">Pulley </text><text styleclass="Body Text">in the graphics-area or </text><text styleclass="Interface">Assembly-Tree</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Interface2">OR</para>
                <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-How-to-Open-a-Dialog-Box" styleclass="SeeAlso">How to Open a dialog</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Element-Header">Pulley dialog</text> is now open.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2"><anchor id="Pulleydialogbox"><keywords><keyword>Pulley dialog<keyword>Release 10</keyword><keyword>Number of Teeth on Pulley</keyword><keyword>Read Only: Drive or Driven Pulley?</keyword><keyword>Read Only: Tooth Pitch</keyword><keyword>Read Only: Belt Length</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Pulley dialog</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:245px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-DIALOG-PULLEY.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[Pulley dialog]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Separator-Header">Pulley Parameters </para>
          <para styleclass="ParameterHeader">Number-of-Teeth</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Parameter">number-of-teeth</text> around the circumference of the <text styleclass="Element">Pulley.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Parameter">Number-of-Teeth</text> and <text styleclass="Parameter">Tooth-Pitch</text> (see <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-MotionPath" styleclass="Element">Motion-Path FB</link>) control the <text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">P.C.D</text> of the <text styleclass="Element">Pulley </text>and the radius of the <text styleclass="Element">Arc</text> in the sketch-path.</para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="ParameterHeader">Pitch-Circle-Diameter (PCD)</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;"> -</text><text styleclass="SeeAlso"> read-only</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The diameter of the Pitch-Circle, which is co-radial with the neutral line of the Belt.</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><equation styleclass="SeeAlso" font-family="Cambria Math" font-size="22"><![CDATA[PCD=\lfrac{\left(#\ Teeth\ on\ Pulley\times Tooth\ Pitch \right)}{\pi}]]></equation></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Separator-Header">Belt Parameters <text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="ParameterHeader">Tooth Pitch</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">- read-only </text><text styleclass="Body Text">( Edit with the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-MotionPath" anchor="BeltToothPitch" styleclass="Body Text">Motion-Path dialog</link><text styleclass="Body Text"> )</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The linear distance between two adjacent teeth on the belt.</para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="ParameterHeader">Belt Length</text><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">- read-only</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The total length of the belt. It is equal to the length of the <text styleclass="VariableName">sketch-loop</text> that wraps around the <text styleclass="Element">Pulleys</text>. </para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The length of the Belt will change as you edit the <text styleclass="Parameter">Number-of-Teeth</text> on a <text styleclass="Element">Pulley</text>,</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">You can select a dimension that will control the <text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">Belt-Length</text> with the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-MotionPath" anchor="BeltToothPitch" styleclass="Element">Motion-Path dialog</link><text styleclass="Element">.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Sprocket Parameters (Apply with Transition-Curve)</para>
